msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.deploy.config.ModelDeploymentConfig:39 of
msgid ""
"Preview version for model deployments, all fields could be changed in the"
" future."
msgstr "模型部署为预览版本，所有字段在未来可能会发生变更。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.deploy.config.ModelDeploymentConfig:41 of
msgid ""
"**User Responsibility Notice**: Users must have a complete understanding "
"of what they are computing and ensure they fully comprehend the "
"implications of their configuration choices. You are responsible for:"
msgstr ""
"**用户责任声明**：用户必须完全理解自己正在执行的计算任务，并确保充分了解"
"其配置选择所带来的影响。您需对以下事项负责："

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.deploy.config.ModelDeploymentConfig:45 of
msgid "Ensuring model compatibility with the specified inference framework"
msgstr "确保模型与指定的推理框架兼容"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.deploy.config.ModelDeploymentConfig:46 of
msgid ""
"Verifying that model files exist and are accessible in the runtime "
"environment"
msgstr "验证模型文件在运行环境中存在且可访问"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.deploy.config.ModelDeploymentConfig:47 of
msgid "Confirming that resource requirements (CPU, memory, GPU) are adequate"
msgstr "确认资源需求（CPU、内存、GPU）充足"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.deploy.config.ModelDeploymentConfig:48 of
msgid "Validating that all dependencies and libraries are properly installed"
msgstr "验证所有依赖项和库均已正确安装"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.deploy.config.ModelDeploymentConfig:49 of
msgid ""
"Understanding the computational behavior and characteristics of your "
"chosen model"
msgstr "理解所选模型的计算行为和特性"

