msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.llm.deploy.config.ModelDeploymentConfig:91 of
msgid ""
"To make this model config working with the ManagedTextGenLLM, you need to"
" provide a custom image with the required dependencies and model files."
msgstr ""
"为了让这个模型配置能够与 ManagedTextGenLLM 配合使用，你需要提供一个包含所"
"需依赖项和模型文件的自定义镜像。"

